List motherduck extensions, their description and status

list_extensions.Rd

Lists available DuckDB extensions, their description, load / installed status and more

Usage

list_extensions(.con)

Arguments

.con

DuckDB connection

Value

tbi

Examples

con <- DBI::dbConnect(duckdb::duckdb())
list_extensions(con)
